In Legends of Atlantis: Exodus, you are transported to the mythic continent of Atlantis. Atlantis is on the verge of its inevitable destruction. You are tasked to help evacuate the ancient Atlanteans from their homes before devastation sinks the cities deep beneath the waves! You will clear obstructed paths, dig canals, frighten away enemies, and build new roads to free the entrapped residents
